body:
### Developer of Python and Javascript
My repo is mostly submissions to the [Center for Open Science](https://github.com/centerforopenscience) plus a bunch of things I've found interesting. Aside from day-to-day development, I occasionally [write about food](http://www.thefoodgeek.com/), [inspire people to create things](http://awesomeography.com/), or tinker around with 3D Printing.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
